OL,3,CFirst patient fitted with new device
OL,4,Cpreventing acid reflux
OL,6,FThe first patients in the UK have had
OL,7,Fa new device implanted to prevent
OL,8,Fsevere acid reflux disease.
OL,10,FDoctors in Southampton became the
OL,11,Ffirst in the UK to use robotic surgery
OL,12,Fto fit the device called RefluxStop.
OL,14,FTeams at University Hospital
OL,15,FSouthampton (UHS) and Imperial College
OL,16,FLondon are the first to carry out the
OL,17,Fprocedure.
