OL,3,CFirst patient fitted with new device
OL,4,Cpreventing acid reflux
OL,6,FFergus Noble, consultant general and
OL,7,Foesophagogastric surgeon at UHS, said:
OL,8,F"GORD can have such a severe impact on
OL,9,Fa person's daily life as not only do
OL,10,Fthey suffer with the physical impact
OL,11,Fwhenever they swallow and eat, but
OL,12,Falso the psychological impact of
OL,13,Fliving with the condition.
OL,15,F"RefluxStop is revolutionary in that
OL,16,Fit is minimally invasive, restores the
OL,17,Flower oesophageal valve to its natural
OL,18,Fposition with no side effects and
OL,19,Foffers some patients a viable
OL,20,Ftreatment option for the first time."
