OL,3,CFirst patient fitted with new device
OL,4,Cpreventing acid reflux
OL,6,FThe mother-of-two, from Southampton,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I began suffering with severe
OL,8,Facid reflux in 2022 and it has
OL,9,Faffected my life in so many ways `
OL,10,Fanything that involves eating or
OL,11,Fdrinking has caused me so much
OL,12,Fanxiety, especially outside of my home.
OL,14,F"The signs are almost immediate with
OL,15,Fan intense pain in my chest as the
OL,16,Freflux comes up the oesophagus and
OL,17,Fburns my throat, often resulting in me
OL,18,Fvomiting, it's been horrendous."
